data.description: **Offer deadline Sunday 1/28/2024 by 6pm **   Location Location Location!  Nestled in the heart of Warren with Warren Consolidated Schools, this fantastic 3 bedroom 2 full bath home is ready for some new owners!!  With a full finished basement, oversized 2.5 car garage with 220v service, fully fenced back yard and great location ~ this home checks all of the boxes!  Updates include furnace and air conditioning new in 2021, new garage roof and so much more!  Spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and skylights providing plenty of natural light is open to the spacious eat-in kitchen with appliances included. Finished basement offers a large family room/recreation area and a large  4th bedroom or office  (no egress window) and another full bathroom.  HUGE utility/storage area with laundry room (newer washer and dryer included). Outside you will find a large deck ~ perfect for entertaining and enjoying summer evenings as well as  the large fully fenced back yard.  Great location near expressways, GM Tech Center, downtown Warren and park/dog park just a short walk away.  BATVAI
